 \___ \ | |  | | | |    | |  | |   | |   | | | |  | || |\ \| |   / /
 ____) || |__| | | |___ | |__| |   | |   | | | |__| || |  \  |  / /__
|_____/  \____/  |_____| \____/    |_|   |_|  \____/ |_|   \_| /_____|

Welcome to the Solutionz INC all-in-one remote configuration script.
